          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>Skylar picked up several items he needed for school. He had $25 in cash. As he was nearing the checkout counter he wondered if he had enough cash to pay the bill. The sales tax is 5%. In the basket he has the following items:</p>"
          ]
        }
